Write a program to find the factorial of a number using functions.

Input Format:

Input consists of 1 integer.

Output Format:

Output consists of a single integer. Refer sample output for formatting details.

Sample Input:

3

Sample Output:


6

//coding

#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int fact(int num)
{
    if(num==0)
    return 1;
    else
    return num*fact(num-1);
}
int main()
{
    int n;
    cin>>n;
    cout<<fact(n);
    
}
